HEADWORD: Sanable
<hw>San"a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>sanabilis</ets>, fr. <ets>sanare</ets> to heal, fr.
<ets>sanus</ets> sound, healthy. See <er>Sane</er>.]</ety> <def>Capable
